A soother is perhaps one of the most common baby care products you can find in households across the world. The soother allows you to comfort and soothe your baby especially when you put your baby to bed or when you need to travel with them
column13: or even during those few minutes between heating your baby\u2019s food and feeding it to them. You could say that a soother is an essentiality for all new parents. But not many parents are aware that they ought to opt for orthodontic soothers because these soothers are shaped to encourage the baby to suck in the same they would if they were breastfeeding. A soother that offers these orthodontic advantages is the Philips Avent Fashion Soother. This soother has an orthodontic
column14: symmetrical and collapsible nipple that aids the natural development of the baby\u2019s palate
column15: teeth and gums even if it ends upside-down in the mouth. Made from soft silicone these 100 per cent BPA-free soothers from Philips are tasteless and odourless

column4: 'title': [u'\n                    Philips Avent Teether Animal Range Front Teeth - Stage 1            ']
column14:
'desc': [u'

Philips Avent Teether Animal Range Front Teeth - Stage 1 (Green) Price: Rs.245

When your baby’s front teeth begin to erupt your baby will want to bite down on things and will try to rub their gums against things to soothe the pain that is caused during teething. The arrival of new teeth brings a completely new sensation in your baby’s mouth and your baby will constantly be trying to rub their erupting front teeth against surfaces to overcome the discomfort. Your baby could hurt themselves by rubbing their teeth and gums against the wrong surface. A safe and hygienic way to help your baby with this teething phase would be by presenting them with the\xa0 Philips Teether. This animal range stage 1 teether has been specially designed for babies whose front teeth have just erupted. The textured surfaces of the teether allow your baby to chew and bite on to enjoy soothing comfort as their teeth being to emerge.

The 100 per cent BPA free teether is safe and can be sterilized for imporved hygiene. The animal teether complies with international standards of safety ensuring that your baby is protected from harm. The appealing design of the teether makes it easy to hold and allows your baby place the teether comfortably in their mouths to enjoy the different pressure levels that the textrured surface provide
column15:
to enjoy maximum comfort. The healthy and hygieneic Philips Teether Animal Range Front Teeth - Stage 1 is suitable to use from birth to 6 months of age and makes a great playtime toy as well.

\n
\n ']
